---
import volunteerImage from "../assets/volunteer-v2.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAFAF8] py-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

    <p class="text-[#5D9C59] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm font-semibold">
      Why Volunteer?
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2F3A45] leading-tight">
      Your time can become a turning point.
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      Volunteering creates steady, human support for children who need guidance, patience and encouragement as they learn.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      Whether you mentor, teach or help connect communities, your presence can help a child feel capable and supported.
    </p>

    <img
      src={volunteerImage.src}
      alt="Volunteer helping children"
      class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover rounded-3xl mt-12"
    />

  </div>
</section>
